00383 /*************
00384  *
00385  * Name:    imtcb
00386  *
00387  * Purpose: QM RR Task control block structure
00388  *
00389  * Members: imdlcb     - DL package control block for logging
00390  *          imicmsgque - IC SMT Message queue
00391  *          imevtpool  - MM pool structure. Contains buffers used
00392  *                       to store information about IM Reponses.
00393  *                       Groups several arguments that can be referenced
00394  *                       by a single handle
00395  *          imdlpool   - MM pool structure. Contains buffers used
00396  *                       for reading download file and packing download file
00397  *                       for sending to the modem
00398  *          imdtxpool  - MM pool structure. Contains buffers used for packing
00399  *                       SDP requests to the modem
00400  *          imrxpool   - MM pool structure. Contains buffers used
00401  *                       to for receiving responses from the modem
00402  *          imrxdatap  - pointer to received data from the modem
00403  *          imdsshell  - dsshell structure for communication to/from the modem
00404  *          imsmp      - pointer to state machine storage
00405  *          imqdl      - storage for download info
00406  *          imhdmemrelp- pointer to memory to be released
00407  *                       (from the HD receive package)
00408  *
00409  * Notes:   none
00410  *
00411  **************/
00412 struct imtcb
00413 {
00414     struct dlusercb    imdlcb;
00415     struct icsmtcb     imicmsgque;
00416     struct mmpool      imevtpool;
00417     struct imevtblock   *imevtblkp;
00418     struct mmpool      imdlpool;
00419     struct mmpool      imtxpool;
00420     struct mmpool      imrxpool;
00421     swi_uint8          *imrxdatap;
00422     struct dsipcshell   imdsshell;
00423     swi_uint8          *imdsmemrelp;
00424     sm_t               *imsmp;
00425     struct imqdl       imqdl;
